{"tid":2065153,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"蘇B：軒達臣將成紅魔No.1","createTime":"2020-06-15T10:51:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-16T07:49:16.000Z","uid":30081,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9a61957add3742cfa68704defe5f30c16093706d","tid":2065153,"uid":30081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T10:51:53.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports】曼聯領隊蘇斯克查認為，軒達臣已證明自己，他朝有日必成紅魔及英格蘭的頭號門將。<br />\n迪基亞近年水準下滑，經常犯錯導致失球，相反軒達臣（ Henderson）近兩季被外借至錫菲聯，表現穩步上揚，不少曼聯球迷都認為，甸軒達臣有力回歸任正選，踢走迪基亞。 蘇斯克查（Ole Gunnar Solskjaer）表示：「今季對軒達臣來說，是一個難能可貴的經驗，他交出令人滿意的表現，證明了自己將來是英格蘭及曼聯的首席門將。」 迪基亞早前續下長約，未知蘇B會否在下季回收軒達臣，讓兩人正面競爭：「我的工作不是保持球員快樂，但他們的工作則是交出表現。軒達臣在過去數年發展很好，作出了不少出色選擇。」"},{"pid":"d7fbd6a2916441a09d2494b680f22abe123e58b6","tid":2065153,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T10:53:35.000Z","msg":"燒賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c3967bc8dd6ed9dc948f9e3f55b70f56291299b","tid":2065153,"uid":46587,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T10:55:51.000Z","msg":"以為利記個位去做曼聯名宿<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c48f867774c8db360184e9f6dc4faa80372177cc","tid":2065153,"uid":47355,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T11:01:44.000Z","msg":"以為肝池又多個曼聯名叔"},{"pid":"01eb4060a4402fdbe038b04df365874b1ff09c1e","tid":2065153,"uid":50744,"like":6,"dislike":5,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T11:07:55.000Z","msg":"成功撲救<br />\n獌:no.1<br />\n<br />\n失兩球<br />\n獌:走啦屌你老母"},{"pid":"c4cb3ec23ba03b369bd1bbf0564e77c1692ec108","tid":2065153,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01eb4060a4402fdbe038b04df365874b1ff09c1e","tid":2065153,"uid":50744,"like":6,"dislike":5,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T11:07:55.000Z","msg":"成功撲救<br />\n獌:no.1<br />\n<br />\n失兩球<br />\n獌:走啦屌你老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T11:10:10.000Z","msg":"兩球？"},{"pid":"376bc88ee462a1feccf7af88f60acce5240e2804","tid